		<h2><span class=""mw-headline"" id=""Trivia"">Trivia</span><span class=""mw-editsection""><span class=""mw-editsection-bracket"">[</span><a href=""/w/Cannonball?section=7&amp;veaction=edit"" class=""mw-editsection-visualeditor"" title=""Edit section: Trivia"">edit</a><span class=""mw-editsection-divider""> | </span><a href=""/w/Cannonball?action=edit&amp;section=7"" title=""Edit section: Trivia"">edit source</a><span class=""mw-editsection-bracket"">]</span></span></h2>
		<ul><li>Cannonballs had a festive override to look like <a href=""https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Christmas_pudding"" class=""extiw"" title=""wikipedia:Christmas pudding"">christmas puddings</a> during the <a href=""/w/2017_Christmas_event/Gallery"" title=""2017 Christmas event/Gallery"">2017</a>, <a href=""/w/2018_Christmas_event/Gallery"" title=""2018 Christmas event/Gallery"">2018</a>, and <a href=""/w/2019_Christmas_event/Gallery"" title=""2019 Christmas event/Gallery"">2019</a> Christmas events. The override had a darker colour in 2019 compared to 2017 and 2018.</li>
		<li>Making a cannonball uses the same animation as when a player buries <a href=""/w/Bones"" title=""Bones"">bones</a>.</li></ul>
